Vizz,Media,is,a,mobile,marketing,service,that,offers,bulk,SMS,solutions,It,allows,users,to,send,bulk,SMS,to,more,than,people,with,one,click,Vizz,Media,supports,both,two,way,SMS,and,Flash,SMS,Users,can,send,single,or,bulk,SMS,directly,through,the,website,or,programmatically,via,REST,or,SMPP,API,The,API,also,allows,users,to,get,delivery,reports,for,their,messages